{"tid":138095,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"( 網絡熱話)麥當勞一連 3 日平食套餐 【附優惠券】Show 畫面即享優惠","createTime":"2017-02-28T10:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T12:16:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ffda0632268706ac4f3409d57b0df0db09545f7","tid":138095,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.e-zone.com.hk/thumbs/735x420/1/channelnews/20170228125948.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.e-zone.com.hk%2Fthumbs%2F735x420%2F1%2Fchannelnews%2F20170228125948.jpg&h=fa17a970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麥當勞推出 HK$5 電子優惠券！這張 HK$5 電子優惠券由 3 月 1 日至 3 月 3 日（星期三至五）都可用，只要在櫃面點餐，跟店員出示這張電子優惠券，即有 HK$5 折扣優惠。更好的是，HK$5 電子優惠券有分超值早晨套餐（供應時間為凌晨 4 時至早上 11 時）及超值套餐（供應時間為早上 11 時至凌晨 4 時）兩款，即是全日 24 小時去麥當勞食好西都有折扣優惠，讀取大圖上的 QR Code 即可得到。<br />\n<br />\n當然，要使用 HK$5 電子優惠券，是有條款須遵守的，如：每次惠顧只限使用一張及只限購買一份套餐、不適用於自動點餐機，以及不適用於山頂、海洋公園、海富中心、沙田馬場、跑馬地馬場、香港國際機場離境大堂及抵港大堂之香港麥當勞這些麥當勞分店。至於超值早晨套餐優惠，不能作購買購買醒晨早餐及開心樂園餐之用；超值套餐優惠，則不能用來購買 HK$24 超值套餐、The Signature Burger 套餐、My Signature Burger 套餐、Create Your Taste 套餐及開心樂園餐。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"http://www.e-zone.com.hk/channelnews.php?id=22830#sthash.FefvafOM.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.e-zone.com.hk%2Fchannelnews.php%3Fid%3D22830%23sthash.FefvafOM.dpuf&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67b5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=4d0a7bb6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.e-zone.com.hk/channelnews.php?id=22830#sthash.FefvafOM.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"1e58c9104b0debaa1080e36950cbd886a5a6f952","tid":138095,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b45b87dad2352fc541773862e7295451153271","tid":138095,"uid":35716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:12:01.000Z","msg":"不能用來購買 HK$24 超值套餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"